name: Insignificant Rebellion
Lore: '''Your fleet is lost. And your friends on the Endor moon will not survive. There is no escape, my young apprentice.''',
Text: 'Use 2 Force to deploy on table. Each time you win a battle, opponent loses 1 Force (cannot be reduced) and stacks lost card here face down. When attempting to cross Luke over (except with Epic Duel), add 3 to total destiny for each card in stack. (Immune to Alter.)',
